==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reversing
<hw>Re*vers"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Serving to effect reversal, as
of motion; capable of being reversed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Reversing engine</b></col>, <cd>a steam engine having a
reversing gear by means of which it can be made to run in either
direction at will.</cd> -- <col><b>Reversing gear</b></col>
<fld>(Mach.)</fld>, <cd>gear for reversing the direction of rotation at
will.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reversion</ent>⟦br⟧
